snippet.title: Sonic Debut - CGS 2021
snippet.description:
This is a ROM hack stylized within Sonic 1's earlier stages, adding in prototype & concept material. Collect coins and avoid a high speed collisions with the varied baddies who will drain you health meter quickly!


Check the game as soon as the 18th hits!
https://chaogameshowcase.wixsite.com/cgs2021/games
